OL,5, A soldier who mistakenly shot a child  
OL,6, while on duty had waited five years for
OL,7, therapy when he took his own life, his 
OL,8, wife has said.                         
OL,10,FGeorge Du Preez, who served as a       
OL,11,Fprivate in Afghanistan, developed      
OL,12,Fpost-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD)  
OL,13,Fafter the incident in 2011.            
OL,15,FHis wife Katriona said he did not know 
OL,16,Fhe was firing at the child at the time.
OL,18,FCwm Taf Morgannwg health board said it 
OL,19,Fwas committed to helping veterans with 
OL,20,Fmental health issues.                  
